data.description: 302 S Mountain offers a unique rehab opportunity for this one of a kind duplex.  Two homes in one with a connecting bedroom, the house is in need of significant repairs interior however exterior, square footage, two in one housing brings tons of opportunity for the right investor.  Will need to be cash sale or rehab loan.  Located in wonderful Lake Lucille community, this HOA comes with small beach and lake to enjoy. Clarkstone school district too!
